Package no.ntnu.idatt1002.app.data

Class User

java.lang.Object
no.ntnu.idatt1002.app.data.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class User extends Object implements Serializable
A User class representing a user with a collection of projects. It provides methods to add, remove, and edit projects, as well as to save the user's data to a file.
